SIMPLE: xerox
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Xerox
<hw>Xe"rox</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From a brand name of
the Xerox corporation.]</ety> <def>A copying machine which copies
graphic matter by the action of light on an electrically charged
photoconductive insulating surface in which the latent image is
developed with a resinous powder.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> xerox, xerographic copier, xerox machine.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A copy made by the xerox process.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> xerox copy.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>xerox</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: xerox
<hw>xe"rox</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To copy a printed
document on a xerographic device.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p> 

<p><ent>xi</ent>⟦br⟧
